description:
This is a 35 minute workout called 'Fat Burning Cardio Low Impact Quiet Barefoot - Full 30-Minute Workout (Cardio Mat Fusion 2)' from the channel jessicasmithtv.
The workout falls under Cardio/Mat and Other/Cardio.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
The workout has a The Groove Session and The Endorphin Wave vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Moderate.

Original workout description: GET OUR LOW IMPACT "WALK ON: 21 DAY WEIGHT LOSS PLAN" ON DVD: ‪http://amzn.to/1HVVgyp‬

GET THE DIGITAL DOWNLOAD: ‪http://bit.ly/1vEMf76‬

Cardio doesn't have to mean loud, joint jarring moves! Join certified instructor Jessica Smith for this non stop session that will keep your heart rate up (and your downstairs neighbors happy) and is gentle enough to be done barefoot (but you'll still work up a good sweat).

Oh, and Peanut the french bulldog makes an appearance in this video too :)

Level: All

Equipment: Mat

Intensity: Moderate

This workout targets the muscles in the thighs, back, calves, glutes, hamstrings, abs, core, hips, shoulders, arms, biceps, triceps, lower back (and more) with moves like:

Lateral Taps
Grand Plies
